title: Typical Weekday Year 2005 PeMS Flows and Speeds
name: Typical Weekday Year 2005 PeMS Flows and Speeds
description:
Metropolitan Transportation Commission
Summary of Caltrans Perfomance Measurement System (PeMS) data.
http://pems.dot.ca.gov/
Includes data from March, April, May, September, October, and November 2005.
Includes data for Tuesdays, Wednesdays, and Thursdays.
Largely excludes imputed data.
Excludes data present only for part-, rather than full-days.
Intended to represent typical day flows and speeds.
Flows aggregated to MTC travel model time periods: EA, 3 am to 6 am; AM, 6 am to 10 am; MD, 10 am to 3 pm; PM, 3 pm to 7 pm; and, EV, 7 pm to 3 am.
Manual off-sets introduced for easier viewing of bi-directional stations.
